@{
    Layout = null;
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>403 - Erişim Engellendi</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e63946, #f1faee);
            color: #1d3557;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 400px;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-radius: 10px;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 60px;
            color: #e63946;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #1d3557;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #457b9d;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #1d3557;
            color: #f1faee;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

            a:hover {
                background-color: #457b9d;
            }

        @@keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>403</h1>
        <h2>Erişim Engellendi</h2>
        <p>Bu sayfaya erişim izniniz bulunmuyor. Lütfen geri dönün veya ana sayfayı ziyaret edin.</p>
        <a href="/">Ana Sayfaya Git</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
